# whitespace-only-line-in-prefix-block

## Input

```
s {
  a 1
  
  b 2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..21
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..21
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    ENTRY@6..10
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "a"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      INTEGER@8..9
        NUMERAL@8..9 "1"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
    SPACE@10..12 "  "
    NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
    SPACE@13..15 "  "
    ENTRY@15..19
      WORD_KEY@15..16
        WORD@15..16 "b"
      SPACE@16..17 " "
      INTEGER@17..18
        NUMERAL@17..18 "2"
      NEWLINE@18..19 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@19..20 "}"
    NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@6..7 "a",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@8..9 "1",
                    },
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@15..16 "b",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@17..18 "2",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@19..20 "}",
        },
    ],
}
